  "body": "\r\n#### Overview of the Issue\r\n\r\nin a resharding process, after migrate replica, the source shard replica is in NonServing state, if the  source shard replica restarted, replica is NonServing now, it will not load scheme infomation, the binlog player will failed,binlog player need the schema information\r\n\r\n#### Reproduction Steps\r\n\r\nstart a resharding workflow, after migrate rdonly and replica, before migrate master, restart the source shard replica, the binlog player will failed\r\n\r\n#### Binary version\r\nmy version is 2.1,other version should the same issue\r\n\r\n",
